I'm just wondering... Why do you zip all your torrents? Why not just take all the eBooks you have and upload them without zipping? It would be easier for us and you wouldn't have to take the time to upload many different torrents. I have seen eBook torrents where there are several files in one torrent and I get to pick which file(s) I wish to DL instead of doing all at once. 
Don't get me wrong.. you have done great uploading all these but its just too much for me to handle.
